config CRYPTO_DEV_QAT_1_7
	tristate "Support for Intel(R) QAT1.7 Devices Select to support Monster Mash devices (mx250b, mx450b)"
	depends on X86 && PCI
	default m
	select ASN1
	help
	  Support for Intel(R) QuickAssist Technology
	  for accelerating crypto and compression workloads for Monsters
	  and Monster Mash boards.

	  To compile this as a module, choose M here. This will compile all QAT1.7
	  supported modules.
